    <item>
      <title>两周后，特朗普和哈里斯陷入僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-10-23/new-poll-has-trump-harris-tied-in-key-states-just-12-days-to-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于摇摆州的民意调查结果非常接近，候选人进入了总统竞选活动的最后几周，为每一位未决选民而战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-10-23/new-poll-has-trump-harris-tied-in-key-states-just-12-days-to-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 22:10:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行观察人士认为 10 月不会有变化，一半人预计 12 月会有所变化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/boj-watchers-see-no-october-move-with-half-expecting-december</link>
      <description><![CDATA[接受彭博调查的大多数经济学家表示，日本央行预计将于下周维持基准利率不变，并于12月或1月加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/boj-watchers-see-no-october-move-with-half-expecting-december</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
