      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/podcast-what-trump-2-0-would-mean-for-the-us-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在本期《选民经济学》中，彭博社主编约翰·米克尔思韦特 (John Micklethwait) 探讨了前总统热衷关税的根源。]]></description>
